snippet.title: Time Rift Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Time Rift is a fast-paced puzzle-shooter. You’re a hacker-turned-security tester, but your skills will only get you so far - to take down global megacorp VaultCo, you’ll have to manipulate the flow of time! ⚡ Get it NOW: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1257660/Time_Rift/
Find us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/timeriftgame
